ed free of encumbrances, it cannot be quashed, imposing a Rs 50,000 cost on landowners for abusing the court process.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/karnataka-high-court-upholds-land-acquisition-for-banashankari-vi-stage-project-in-bengaluru/131544021?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-70844/131544021.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}